      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "qIb60N76KKvQ-Jb_zbmz8",
      "originalText": "Execute pending migrations  against the `ponder_sync` database schema, \nas per the config returned from the Ponder's `buildMigrationProvider()` call.",
